N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 ยง 80.121 - Rules and regulations

State Regulations

Rules, regulations and determinations, when made and promulgated by the commissioner, shall be the rules and regulations and determinations of the department, and, until modified or rescinded, shall have the force and effect of law. Notes
